# ⚙️ Installation & Setup

## 1️⃣ Clone the Repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/brodapeethar/groupie-tracker.git
```

---

## 2️⃣ Navigate Into the Project

```bash
cd groupie-tracker
```

---

## 3️⃣ Initialize Go Modules

```bash
go mod tidy
```

---

## 4️⃣ Run the Application

```bash
go run .
```

---

# 🌐 Open in Browser

Visit:

```bash
http://localhost:7070
```

---

# 🔗 API Used

This project uses the Groupie Tracker API:

```bash
https://groupietrackers.herokuapp.com/api
```

Endpoints used:

| Endpoint | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `/artists` | Artist information |
| `/relation` | Concert locations and dates |

