# 🔍 Search & Filtering Logic

The application dynamically filters artists based on:

- artist names
- member names
- creation dates
- album years

This is handled server-side using query parameters.

Example:

```bash
/?search=queen
```

---

# ❌ Error Handling

The application includes custom error pages for:

| Error | Description |
|---|---|
| 400 | Invalid artist ID |
| 404 | Page not found |
| 500 | Internal server error |

---

# 📱 Responsive UI

The UI adapts to different screen sizes using:

- CSS Grid
- Flexbox
- media queries

